<text><body><cb:div>
<milestone n="1" unit="juan"/>
<pb n="0144a" xml:id="I01.0056.0144a" ed="I"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0144a01"/><cb:docNumber>No. 56</cb:docNumber>
<lb ed="I" n="0144a02"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"/><cb:jhead><title>馬敬賢五十人等造像記</title></cb:jhead></cb:juan><cb:div>
<pb n="0145a" xml:id="I01.0056.0145a" ed="I"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0145a01"/><p xml:id="pI01p0145a0101" cb:type="pre">．．．族</p></cb:div><cb:div>
<pb n="0145b" xml:id="I01.0056.0145b" ed="I"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0145b01"/><p xml:id="pI01p0145b0101" cb:type="pre">　□齊□保三年歲在壬申四月廿三日建。
<lb ed="I" n="0145b02"/>　夫至理沖<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">凝</unclear>。絕<note n="0145001" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30830"/>＝詮【史】</note><note n="0145001" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30830"/>【佛拓】，詮【史】</note><app n="0145001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">詮</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30830"/></rdg></app><note n="0145002" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30831"/>＝數【史】</note><note n="0145002" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30831"/>【佛拓】，數【史】</note><app n="0145002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">數</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30831"/></rdg></app>之表。法身<note n="0145003" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30560"/>＝虛【史】</note><note n="0145003" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30560"/>【佛拓】，虛【史】</note><app n="0145003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">虛</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30560"/></rdg></app>洞。
<lb ed="I" n="0145b03"/>　超有无之境。是故如來。欲使迷駕迴
<lb ed="I" n="0145b04"/>　<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">輪</unclear>。異路改轍。故託跡形名。以曉未悟。邑主
<lb ed="I" n="0145b05"/>　馬敬賢合邑五十人等。各捨家珍。敬造石
<lb ed="I" n="0145b06"/>　像一區。雕<note n="0145004" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">餝＝飾【史】</note><note n="0145004" resp="ihp" type="mod">餝【佛拓】，飾【史】</note><app n="0145004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">飾</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】">餝</rdg></app><note n="0145005" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">庄＝莊【史】</note><note n="0145005" resp="ihp" type="mod">庄【佛拓】，莊【史】</note><app n="0145005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">莊</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】">庄</rdg></app>嚴。<note n="0145006" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30329"/>＝鏤【史】</note><note n="0145006" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30329"/>【佛拓】，鏤【史】</note><app n="0145006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">鏤</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30329"/></rdg></app>形精麗。伏願　皇帝。
<lb ed="I" n="0145b07"/>　國祚永延。師僧父母。超越三界。託趣道場。
<lb ed="I" n="0145b08"/>　彌勒出世。故能刊石鐫芳。用宣賢劫。
<lb ed="I" n="0145b09"/>當陽像主馬雄</p></cb:div><cb:div>
<pb n="0145c" xml:id="I01.0056.0145c" ed="I"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0145c01"/><p xml:id="pI01p0145c0101" cb:type="pre">．．．<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">連</unclear>　　清信．．．
<lb ed="I" n="0145c02"/>．．．奴　　清信江要姬
<lb ed="I" n="0145c03"/>．．．□　　清信□堂女
<lb ed="I" n="0145c04"/>．．．養
<lb ed="I" n="0145c05"/>．．．安生</p></cb:div></cb:div>
